rows.label: qev025805_MSG0004
rows.name:
There are those who would criticize our activities here.
But who among them can end the suffering of these
poor Ma-non?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025805_MSG0005
rows.name:
Not one. All the words in the world are empty air next
to the power of one miracle. Such is our belief.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025805_MSG0006
rows.name:
If you ever find yourself in need of a miracle,
our doors shall be open to you.[ST:wait ]
